\begin{align*}(1)\;\;\;\sin 2x&=2\sin x\cos x\\ (2)\;\;\;\cos 2x&=\cos^2x-\sin^2x=2\cos^2x-1=1-2\sin^2x\end{align*}
\sin 4x=2\sin2x\cos2x=2(2\sin x\cos x)(2\cos^2x-1)
